@startuml
skinparam dpi 300
title Register Restaurant

start
:Open Restaurant Registration Form;
note right : Step 1 - Restaurant Owner opens the Registration Form
:Enter restaurant details \n(name, address, phone, image);
note right : Step 2 - Owner enters restaurant details
:Enter menu items \n(name, description, price, image);
note right : Step 3 - Owner enters menu item details
:Submit registration form;
note right : Step 4 - Owner submits the registration form
:Validate required fields;
note right : Step 5 - System validates that all required fields are filled in
if(Field valid?) then (no)
    :Display error message;
    note right : Step 6a - System displays error message
    stop
else (yes)
endif
:Create restaurant record;
note right : Step 6b - System creates a new restaurant record
:Create menu item records;
note right : Step 7 - System creates menu item records for the restaurant
:Display registration success;
note right : Step 8 - System notifies owner of successful registration;\nRestaurant is now visible to customers
stop

@enduml